# Deliverables go to the Desktop folder

Every user-facing document the agent produces (pitch decks, PDFs, PPTX, DOCX,
XLSX, brochures, reports, exports) MUST be copied to:

`/Users/musaibrahim/Desktop/PalmCare Documents/`

- Keep the working/source files in the repo as usual (e.g. `marketing/...`),
  but always place a copy of the final artifact in that Desktop folder.
- Use clear versioned filenames (e.g. `PalmCare_Deck_v5.pdf`).
- If the folder is missing, create it.
